From fd002aa554a486fc37892953a1fab827459b45e4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Thu, 5 Mar 2026 06:52:41 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 02/25] Patch stock Chromium for libtermsurf_chromium

Eight patches, surgical and tight:
A hidden window, a constructor's right,
CALayer callbacks, cursor hooks too,
The minimum Chromium needs to do.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
---
 BUILD.gn                                         |  1 +
 .../renderer_host/render_widget_host_impl.cc     |  7 +++++++
 .../renderer_host/render_widget_host_impl.h      |  9 +++++++++
 .../renderer_host/render_widget_host_view_mac.h  |  9 +++++++++
 .../renderer_host/render_widget_host_view_mac.mm | 10 +++++++++-
 content/shell/browser/shell_devtools_frontend.h  |  7 +++++--
 .../shell/browser/shell_platform_delegate_mac.mm | 16 ++++++++++++++--
 content/shell/common/shell_switches.h            |  5 +++++
 8 files changed, 59 insertions(+), 5 deletions(-)

